description: Xilisoft AVI to DVD Converter is easy-to-use DVD authoring software and DVD Converter with high quality and fast burning speed. It can convert AVI, DivX, MPEG etc. to DVD-Video discs which is playable on portable/home DVD players. It allows you to specify NTSC or PAL, 4:3 or 16:9 video aspect ratio, title miniature, and select a segment to burn. In addition to burning DVD discs, you can also choose to save files as DVD folder or ISO files. The software provides lots of background templates so that you can create your own DVD menu to fit different occasions. Totally supports DVD-R, DVD+R, DVD-RW, DVD+RW, DVD-5 and DVD-9.
